    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In &quot;Looks About Right,&quot; players step into the shoes of an upcoming forger in a thrilling art simulation game. Your mission is to replicate famous artworks and currency and legal documents with incredible precision. Will you become the ultimate counterfeiter, or will your art fall flat? Get ready to test your skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/18189765b8406f31cf5722510aed2bf6.poster.avif?t=1763014629\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/18189765b8406f31cf5722510aed2bf6.webm?t=1763014629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/18189765b8406f31cf5722510aed2bf6.mp4?t=1763014629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are up for a real test of skill you can try out our Challenge Mode which you need to score 100%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/ef4b506b1d33627b6bfb21c739cc5ccb.poster.avif?t=1763014629\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/ef4b506b1d33627b6bfb21c739cc5ccb.webm?t=1763014629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/ef4b506b1d33627b6bfb21c739cc5ccb.mp4?t=1763014629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you wanna see how good your art would do in this world head over to our sandbox mode where you can draw your own art and sell it for money in an auction full of rich people </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/ec990916d079c9ba2e84305a8be59800.poster.avif?t=1763014629\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/ec990916d079c9ba2e84305a8be59800.webm?t=1763014629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254470/extras/ec990916d079c9ba2e84305a8be59800.mp4?t=1763014629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
